NK131(do)002:1: // rtsod bzlog gnam lcags 'brug brgya dgod pa'i nga ro yod /
NK131(do)002:3: grangs med bskal pa rgya mtshor snying stobs chen po'i gru bcas te //
NK131(do)002:4: brgal dka' srid mtsho duhkha'i rba rlangs 'khrug las pha rol phyin //
NK131(do)002:5: sku gsum yid bzhin mchog ldan lhar bcas 'gro ba'i ded dpon che //
NK131(do)002:6: rnam 'dren zas gtsang sras kyi zhabs la byang chub bar du 'dud //
NK131(do)002:7: rgyal kun mkhyen brtse nus pa'i rnam rol las //
NK131(do)002:8: thub bstan nyin mor byed la ston pa dngos //
NK131(do)002:9: ge sar pad+ma'i rtse las nyer sprul ba //
NK131(do)002:10: mtsho skyes pad+ma rgyal po phyag gi gnas //
NK131(do)002:11: gang gi rjes 'jug snyom las b+hu su kur //
NK131(do)002:12: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i khur gyis dben gnas yang //
NK131(do)002:13: log lta'i mun pas gtibs pa'i skal ngan dag /
NK131(do)002:14: brtse bar 'dor bar ma nus 'di skad spel //
NK131(do)002:15: mkhas btsun bzang phyir rgyu 'bras blang dor la //
NK131(do)002:16: zhib mor dpyad na thub pa'i lung dang mthun //
NK131(do)002:17: chos spangs sgrib pas sbags kyang tshul 'chos kyis //
NK131(do)002:18: 'chad rtsod rtsom par 'dod pa bdud kyi las //
NK131(do)002:19: ston pa'i rgyal ba 'gran bral o rgyan rje'i //
NK131(do)002:20: gsang gsum phrin las mi zad rgyan 'khor che'i //
NK131(do)002:21: spyod yul rnam par 'phrul la rtog brtags kyis //
NK131(do)002:22: dgag bsgrub nam mkha'i tshad gzungs ji bzhin no //
NK131(do)002:23: 'on kyang thun mong mdzad pa 'ga' zhig la //
NK131(do)002:24: log rtog zhugs 'dis 'gro ba mang po dag /
NK131(do)002:25: log pa'i lam du 'jug 'di bkag phyir du //
NK131(do)002:26: bdag gi lhag bsam dag pas 'dir bshad bya //
NK131(do)002:27: de yang rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che'i bya
NK131(do)002:28: ba mdzad pa la gzhan drin mi 'jog pa'i mkhas
NK131(do)002:29: mchog rme ru mkhan chen phun tshogs rgyal mtshan pa'i
NK131(do)002:30: zhal snga nas kyis thang yig la dgos gnas kyi
NK131(do)002:31: gzhi dag 'god par mdzad pa'i skabs /
NK131(do)002:33: rgya ma grwa tshang gi bla ma rtse bstun rong pa'i rab 'byams pa'i ngag bkod nas /
NK131(do)002:34: de rjes nyid rang gis kyang dpyad gzhi 'ga' mdzad pa gnyis las /
NK131(do)002:36: bde ba can gyi zhing bkod skabs /
NK131(do)002:37: rgyal blon med par bshad nas /
NK131(do)002:38: de rjes 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po bzang po mchog ces pa 'gal zhe na /
NK131(do)002:39: spyir bde can dag pa'i zhing khams yin pas /
NK131(do)002:40: rtag brtan ther zug gi 'dzin pa med par mdo rgyud las bshad cing /
NK131(do)002:41: de mtshungs rgyal blon yod med kyang gdul bya'i dbang gi sna tshogs zhig ste /
NK131(do)002:42: dper na rje btsun gtsang kha pa chen po'i bde can zhing bkod kyi rnam bshad las kyang /
NK131(do)002:43: sems can bde ba can du skye ba'i smon lam
NK131(do)002:44: btab pa rnams smon lam gyi stobs kyis zhing der
NK131(do)002:45: skye la the tshom skyes pa rnams /
NK131(do)002:46: me tog sbubs su skyes kyang yun ring por kha mi bye bar bshad pas /
NK131(do)002:47: de yang bde ba can na sdug bsngal yod dam zhes smra'am /
NK131(do)002:48: kho bos bsams na de dag drang nges ldem dgongs
NK131(do)002:49: kyi dbang gi sna tshogs kyi spyod yul du blta
NK131(do)002:51: bde ba can na rgyal blon med ces pa /
NK131(do)002:52: phal pa'i rgyal blon khrims dang khral 'u lag sogs
NK131(do)002:53: byed pa'i rigs de 'dra med par dgongs pa yin
NK131(do)002:55: khyod kyis srog chags gsad par bya //
NK131(do)002:56: rdzun gyi tshig kyang smra bar bya //
NK131(do)002:57: zhes sogs gsungs pa yang dngos bstan du khas mi len pa dang 'dra /
NK131(do)002:58: dkyil 'khor gyi lha ltar rnam pa gtso 'khor du
NK131(do)002:59: bstan kyang don la mchog dman med pa'i sprul pa'i
NK131(do)002:60: rgya blon med ces khas ma blangs te /
NK131(do)002:61: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po bzang po mchog lta bu yin no //
NK131(do)002:63: myang 'das kyi shes byed 'god pa na /
NK131(do)002:64: bcom ldan 'das la 'od srungs dang gcung dga' bo
NK131(do)002:65: ma gtogs zhes kun dga' bo med par bshad na
NK131(do)002:67: ma 'gags pa dang kun dga' bo rnams la nga
NK131(do)002:68: ni yongs su mya ngan las 'ada'o zhes kun dga'
NK131(do)002:70: tshig gcig la yang 'gal ba gnyis 'dug /
NK131(do)002:74: 'od srungs dang gcung dga' bo ma gtogs pa /
NK131(do)002:75: dge slong gi dge 'dun brgya phrag bcus bskor nas /
NK131(do)002:79: kun dga' rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK131(do)002:80: zhes bshad pa ma rtogs med pas /
NK131(do)002:81: zhib tu ma dpyad par 'os tshod tshig 'khyams kyi
NK131(do)002:82: dam chos sun phyung ba la phan yon ci zhig
NK131(do)002:83: yod / log rtog ngan pa'i sems kho nar gyur
NK131(do)002:84: tshe gzhung lugs kun la 'gal 'du mang bas zhi
NK131(do)002:85: bde byang chub kyi sems la gnas par mdzad na
NK131(do)002:87: sa steng thams cad ko g.yog tu //
NK131(do)002:88: de la ko bas ci la longs //
NK131(do)002:89: lham mthil tsam gyi ko bas ni //
NK131(do)002:92: khro ba'i sems gcig chom gyur na //
NK131(do)002:97: stong lung gzhong pa'i brag gdong na zhes /
NK131(do)002:98: gzhong pa lha chu brag gdong na yod par bshad
NK131(do)002:99: pas ming tsam gyi yang ma mthong ba 'dug ste
NK131(do)002:100: / zhes gsungs pa de yang bab col gyi bka' skyon te /
NK131(do)002:102: stod lung gzhong pa'i mda' ru mjal tsam na //
NK131(do)002:103: drod bar 'debs pa'i ja chu ma rnyed nas //
NK131(do)002:104: o rgyan chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi //
NK131(do)002:105: stod lung gzhong pa'i gdong la phyag mkhar btsugs //
NK131(do)002:106: zhes gsung pa ma rtogs brag gdong zhes ma gsungs la /
NK131(do)002:108: gdong zhes pa spyi mtshan yin mod brag gdong du
NK131(do)002:109: khas ma blangs kyang brag gdong zhes smra zhes skur
NK131(do)002:111: rang nyid ngan par ston pa'i mdzad pa yin na ni smos ma dgos te /
NK131(do)002:113: rang dma' rang gis ma phab na //
NK131(do)002:114: brgya byin gyis kyang ga la phebs //
NK131(do)002:115: chu mig rang nyid ma skams na //
NK131(do)002:116: sa yis mnan kyang non mi 'gyur //
NK131(do)002:119: rgyas pa 'bum ni klu yul gter du sbas //
NK131(do)002:120: nyi khri brgya byin yul du gter du sbas //
NK131(do)002:121: khri pa lha min yul du gter du sbas //
NK131(do)002:123: yum sras bcu bdun ma li'i yul du sbas zhes phyi ma bshad tsa na snga ma brjed pa'am /
NK131(do)002:124: yum sras bcu bdun gyi mdo ngos ma zin pa gang rung du 'gyur zhes pa'i lan ni /
NK131(do)002:125: yum sras bcu bdun ma li'i yul du cha tshang bar sbas shing /
NK131(do)002:126: gzhan rnams 'dul zhing kha 'thor ba so sor sbas pas 'gal ba ci yod /
NK131(do)002:127: 'di la lung rigs kyi lan 'debs pa'i yul du gyur pa zhig mi 'dug pas /
NK131(do)002:128: phal gtam ltar bshad na thugs su 'bab par 'gyur te /
NK131(do)002:129: go rgyu med pa'i glang po la //
NK131(do)002:130: rgyal po'i bka' las dbyug pa btsan //
NK131(do)002:132: dper na khyim zhig na bka' 'gyur tshar gcig dang /
NK131(do)002:133: 'bum tshar gcig thol du yod pa zhig na /
NK131(do)002:134: bka' 'gyur gyi nang na 'bum yod pas /
NK131(do)002:135: khyod la 'bum thol ba mi rigs zhes gashe'am /
NK131(do)002:136: 'di ni dgos pa nyin skar las kyang nyung bas mkhas pa'i sgros ma yin no //
NK131(do)002:138: mchod rten sa dang brag dang ri sogs gter gnas
NK131(do)002:139: lha klu sogs gter srung mdo sde sogs gter chos
NK131(do)002:140: ma 'ongs pa can 'byin lung bstan pas gter ston
NK131(do)002:141: sogs gsal por bstan pa kho bo'i blo gros kyi
NK131(do)002:142: mig chung ngus brtags tshe mthong bas spyir zab gter
NK131(do)002:143: dang dgos gsung rab lha klu mi rnams kyi gnas
NK131(do)002:144: su gter du sbas pa 'di yid ches kyi gnas
NK131(do)002:145: su rtogs la / de lta bu'i tshul rnams rgyas par mnyan par 'dod na /
NK131(do)002:146: kho bo la bka' 'gyur ro cog yongs su rdzogs pa'i lung rgyun yod pas /
NK131(do)002:147: de dag gsan phyir spyod cig dang /
NK131(do)002:148: the tshom gyi 'ching ba las grol zhing /
NK131(do)002:149: bgres khar thugs bskyed phul du phyin pa thon par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)002:151: nga ni mngal skyes ma yin rdzus skyes yin //
NK131(do)002:152: rgyal po mngal skyes yin pas nga nyid che //
NK131(do)002:154: bardzusa skyes yin pa tsam gyis lhag na /
NK131(do)002:155: dmyal ba dang yi dwags kyang lhag par 'gyur zhes dang /
NK131(do)002:156: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngal sgo 'grim //
NK131(do)002:157: grangs med gsum du bsod nams bsags //
NK131(do)002:158: zhes tshe gcig la sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas de /
NK131(do)002:159: grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags pa'i sangs rgyas las
NK131(do)002:160: lhag par bshad 'dug pas de gnyis la myur bul
NK131(do)002:162: sangs rgyas zin pa la lhag mi lhag gi khyad par ni med /
NK131(do)002:164: mngal skyes dang rdzus skyes gnyis /
NK131(do)002:167: skabs 'gar bardzusa skyes lhag tshul sogs bkag pa med par lung las bshad la /
NK131(do)002:168: skabs 'dir bod kyi 'dre srin gdug can sogs 'dul phyir /
NK131(do)002:169: de dag bardzusa skyes ma rtogs mngal skyes kyis mi thul ba la dgongs te /
NK131(do)002:170: bardzusa skyes che tshul gsung pa yin te /
NK131(do)002:171: slob dpon +aar+ya de wa mu stegs ma khol 'dul phyir bardzusa skyes su byon pa lta bu'o //
NK131(do)002:172: yang dmyal ba yi dwags thams cad bardzusa skyes yin pa'i mtha' yang chod par mi nus te /
NK131(do)002:173: yi dwags mkha' la rgyu ba'i 'byung po mthu bo
NK131(do)002:174: che bdud btsan rgyal po sogs 'ga' zhig la rigs
NK131(do)002:175: rus pha ma sogs yod par lung las bshad cing
NK131(do)002:176: rig pa tshad mas kyang grub pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)002:177: yang tshe gcig la sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas de
NK131(do)002:178: grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags pa'i sangs rgyas las
NK131(do)002:180: spyir rgyu lam gnyis lam byed kyi dbang las de
NK131(do)002:181: gnyis sangs rgyas tshul gyi rnam dbye bshad pa tsam
NK131(do)002:183: phyi ru nyan thos theg pa rim pa dgu bshad pa la mi 'thad pa mang ba zhig 'dug /
NK131(do)002:185: spyir nyan thos la sogs theg rim dgu yod tshul bshad pa las /
NK131(do)002:186: nyan thos rang thog na theg dgu yod ces ma yin no //
NK131(do)002:187: de ltar theg dgu'i 'thad pa grangs nges sogs lung
NK131(do)002:188: rigs dang sbyar ba rgyas par bshad du yod kyang
NK131(do)002:189: / skabs 'dir rtsod pa'i dus yin cing /
NK131(do)002:191: skabs su ma bab phyir gsang sgrogs su 'gyur bas re zhig bzhag go /
NK131(do)002:192: gnyis pa mkhan chen nyid rang gi dgos gnad kyi dang por /
NK131(do)002:194: nyin dang mtshan gyi ming yang mi grags btsal gyis
NK131(do)002:195: mi rnyed pah zhes nyin mtshan gyi tha snyad med
NK131(do)002:196: par bshad nas / le'u de'i 'og tsam nah rnam
NK131(do)002:197: par dag pa'i me tog de nyid la nyin mtshan
NK131(do)002:198: rgyun du thun bzung bsrung bar gyur sprel lo dpyid
NK131(do)002:199: zla ra ba'i tshes gcig nyin zhes nyin mtshan bshad
NK131(do)002:200: pa dran pas ma zin pa 'dra bsam /
NK131(do)002:202: dran pas ma zin pa su la 'byung 'chad dka' ba ste /
NK131(do)002:203: spyir bde can zhing bkod kyi bgag bzhag mdo tsam
NK131(do)002:204: thog ma nyid du smos zin pas des khyab mod
NK131(do)002:205: / khyad par nyin mtshan gyi rnam dbye ni /
NK131(do)002:206: mi rnams la nyin mtshan 'di ltar du snang la /
NK131(do)002:207: lha rnams la chos mngon par nyi ma 'char nub sogs kyi nyin mtshan lha la med kyang /
NK131(do)002:208: gnyid bro mi bro sogs kyi nyin mtshan gyi dbye ba bshad pa'ang 'dug la /
NK131(do)002:210: rgyal po'i khab na khyim bdag shin tu bzang zhes
NK131(do)002:211: gsung ba mu stegs kyi sbyin bdag zhig yod pa
NK131(do)002:212: de'i chung ma la mngal chags pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)002:213: bcom ldan 'das phyogs der gsheg pa mthong nas /
NK131(do)002:215: bdag gi mchis 'brang 'di la bu batsa'am /
NK131(do)002:218: bu skye ste rigs gsal ba dang /
NK131(do)002:219: lha dang mi'i bde ba myongs nas nga'i bstan pa
NK131(do)002:220: la rab tu byung ste dgra bcom par 'gyur ro
NK131(do)002:222: gcer bu pas thos te de rtsis la mkhas pas de ltar 'byung ba shes kyang /
NK131(do)002:223: log par bsgyur te bshad pas khyim bdag bslad de
NK131(do)002:224: chung ma la sman ma yin pa sbyin shing bsku
NK131(do)002:225: mnyes kyang / sems can srid pa tha ma pa'i mthus ma shi bar /
NK131(do)002:226: mthar chung ma bsad de shi ba ltar byas te phung po dur khrod du bskyal ba'i tshe /
NK131(do)002:227: mer bsregs pas lte ba'i nye skor ma tshig pa btol te pad+ma'i snying po las khye'u skyes pa /
NK131(do)002:228: ston pas longs zhes gsungs kyang /
NK131(do)002:229: pha mu stegs kyis slad pas ma blangs pa /
NK131(do)002:231: gzugs can snying pos bskyangs pa /
NK131(do)002:233: pha shi zhing khye'u me skyes kyi khyim gzung bas /
NK131(do)002:234: thub pa'i lung bzhin mi'i dpal myong bar gyur la /
NK131(do)002:236: khrus ras rlung gis khyer ba rgyal po'i khang thog
NK131(do)002:237: tu lhung ba lha'i gos su 'khrul pa me skyes
NK131(do)002:239: rgyu des rgyal po la khyim bstan par khas blangs te /
NK131(do)002:240: khyim du rgyal po gdan drangs pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)002:241: phyi dang bar gyi bran mo rnams chung ma yin
NK131(do)002:242: ma zhes rgyal pos dris pa la bran mo yin
NK131(do)002:243: tshul brjod pa dang bar sgo'i nang bee d+aur+ya'i gzhi
NK131(do)002:244: la ri mo sna tshogs kyi bkra ba /
NK131(do)002:246: chung mas rgyal po la phyag byas pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)002:247: rgyal po'i gos la du ba'i dri bro bas mchi ma 'dzag pa dang /
NK131(do)002:248: de lta bu'i mi las 'das par dpal 'byor gyi /
NK131(do)002:249: me skyes kyi khyim du zhag bdun 'das kyang /
NK131(do)002:250: rgyal po zhag gcig las ma song snyam pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)002:251: blon po rnams kyi sbran te ma skyes dgra yab gdan 'dren du btang bas /
NK131(do)002:252: rgyal pos bu khyod kyi zhag gcig gi bya ba yang mi byed dam /
NK131(do)002:255: rgyal pos mi skyes la smras pa /
NK131(do)002:256: zhag bdun yin nam yin lags so //
NK131(do)002:259: me tog kha bye ba dang zum pa dang nor
NK131(do)002:260: bu 'od 'bar ba dang bya skad 'byin mi 'byin
NK131(do)002:261: las shes so // zhes smras so //
NK131(do)002:262: me skyes mthar bstan pa la rab tu byung zhing /
NK131(do)002:263: dgra bcom thob pa sogs rgyas par bshad pa ltar yin no //
NK131(do)002:265: lha phal pa rnams kyi mthu la yang nyin gyi dbye tshul de bzhin yod na /
NK131(do)002:266: bde ba can sprul pa'i zhing khams yin pas rtag brten ther zug gi nyin mtshan tha snyad med /
NK131(do)002:267: skabs 'dir nyin mtshan thun bzung zhes pa /
NK131(do)002:268: res mos kyi thun bzung ste me tog bsrungs pa la /
NK131(do)002:269: mi yul ltar mtshungs pa'i tshig gis brtags pa yin /
NK131(do)002:270: dper na rgya gar na gnam bskos zhes pa'i tha snyad med kyang /
NK131(do)002:271: lo ts+aa ba rnams kyi don thob kyi dbang du
NK131(do)002:272: byas nas rgyal po chen po la gnam bskos zhes
NK131(do)002:274: de ltar log rtog 'byung ba yang /
NK131(do)002:275: thos pa phyogs rer lhung ba'i skyon yin pas /
NK131(do)002:276: thos bsam rgya mtsho lta bu mdzad na /
NK131(do)002:277: log rtog gu dog gi shes bya'i 'ching ba las
NK131(do)002:278: rtsod pa'i sgro btags pa dang bral bar 'gyur ro
NK131(do)002:280: skye ba pad+ma'i steng nas bardzusa te skye ba las /
NK131(do)002:281: skye ba gzhan gyi ming yang mi grags btsal kyang mi rnyed pa /
NK131(do)002:282: zhes skye gnas gzhan med par bshad /
NK131(do)002:284: btsun mo stong yod sras ni gcig kyang med //
NK131(do)002:285: ces 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po bzang po mchog
NK131(do)002:286: gi btsun mo la sras yong dgos pa 'dra ba
NK131(do)002:288: mngal skyes zhig yod pa yang 'dra sems /
NK131(do)002:289: zhes pa'i lan ni spyir bde ba can du bardzusa skyes ma rtogs mngal skyes med par bshad kyang /
NK131(do)002:290: skabs 'dir rgyal po bzang po mchog gi bla mchod
NK131(do)002:291: kyi tshul ston pa dang sras kyi ded mdzad pa
NK131(do)002:292: sogs kyi rgyu mtshan gyi btsun mo stong yod la
NK131(do)002:293: sras med pa sogs kyi tshul ni dkon pa bstan
NK131(do)002:295: sems can khengs can rnams 'dul phyir ston pa 'od
NK131(do)002:296: dpag med kyi dbu gtsug las 'od zer dmar po
NK131(do)002:297: sprul pa yin / thang yig las /
NK131(do)002:298: zhing de'i sangs rgyas 'od dpag med pa yi 'jig
NK131(do)002:299: rten rgyal po la sogs dregs pa can khengs sems
NK131(do)002:300: che bas bcings rnams 'dul ba'i phyir pad+mo bde ba
NK131(do)002:301: can gyi zhing khams su dbu gtsug 'od zer dmar
NK131(do)002:302: po rgyal por sprul mtshan ni 'khor los sgyur rgyal
NK131(do)002:303: bzang po mchog ces gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)002:304: rgyal po bzang po mchog ni sprul pa ma rtogs
NK131(do)002:305: rang rgyud pa min phyir tshul ston pa'i mdzad pa
NK131(do)002:306: yin la / 'on kyang 'di dag 'jig rten mthun 'jug mdzad pa ma rtogs /
NK131(do)002:307: tshad ma rtag brtan ther zug zhig ma yin te /
NK131(do)002:308: dper na thub dbang yang yum sgyu 'phrul ma gso
NK131(do)002:309: sbyong mdzad pa'i lhums su zhugs par bzhed pa la
NK131(do)002:310: / 'khrig pa la ma brten nas yab yum kyang
NK131(do)002:311: mi 'thad pa lhums su yang 'jug mi nus shing
NK131(do)002:313: 'khrig pa spyad na yum gyi gso sbyong nyams pas /
NK131(do)002:314: de rnams kyang 'gal zhes rgol bar byas na ji ltar yong /
NK131(do)002:317: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku //
NK131(do)002:318: 'khrig pa la ni brten med kyang //
NK131(do)002:319: yab dang yum du ston mdzad la //
NK131(do)002:321: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun par /
NK131(do)002:322: 'di dag kyang de'i rjes su mthun nam snyam mo //
NK131(do)002:323: 'on kyang sangs rgyas byang sems kyis rnam thar la
NK131(do)002:324: dad pa dang dag snang ches pa'i skyon byung tshe
NK131(do)002:325: sku nyid la bzod par gsol lo //
NK131(do)002:326: yang ru t+r+aa'i byung ba 'chad pa'i skabs su /
NK131(do)002:327: sum cu rtsa gsum dga' ldan lha yul na //
NK131(do)002:329: dga' ldan lha yul sum cu rtsa gsum na med
NK131(do)002:330: pa 'jig rten rang kha bas kyang rtogs pa 'dra
NK131(do)002:332: spyir dga' ldan sum cu rtsa na dga' ldan sogs 'brel mtshungs su yod phyir bshad pa yin la /
NK131(do)002:333: gzhan dga' ldan yid dga' chos 'dzin dag zhing yin pas /
NK131(do)002:334: drang don ltar na ru tra der 'gro mi thub
NK131(do)002:335: ru tra rang gi snang ba la sum cu rtsa
NK131(do)002:337: lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar po mthong zhing ngan
NK131(do)002:338: sems kyis pang par blangs te mar bsgyur ba'i snang
NK131(do)002:340: bsam sbyor des ru tra'i bsod nams kyi mtha' btul te rta phag gis myur du bsgral ba yin /
NK131(do)002:342: dus gsum pa yi sangs rgyas rnams //
NK131(do)002:343: dgra bos bsad par bsams nas ni //
NK131(do)002:345: dam pa tog dkar la ma gnod kyang ru tra'i rang gi bsod nams la gnod pa yin /
NK131(do)002:346: rgyu mtshan de la brten nas /
NK131(do)002:347: sum cu rtsa gsum la dga' ldan gyi sgras btags pa yin mod /
NK131(do)002:348: de btags pa la skyon yod na /
NK131(do)002:350: khams gsum pa yi ral gri che //
NK131(do)002:351: zhes rdo rje la ral gri'i sgra btags pa la skyon yong ngam //
NK131(do)002:352: nges don ltar na lha sbyin dang legs kar sogs kyang ston pa'i sprul pa bzhin /
NK131(do)002:353: ru tra la'ang de mtshungs kyi dbye ba 'byed rgyu yod /
NK131(do)002:354: yang dam pa tog dkar chos stan mthong ba nas
NK131(do)002:355: pang pas 'ub bsdus mi mjed 'jig rten dor zhes
NK131(do)002:356: bshad 'dug pa / dga' ldan mi mjed 'jig rten
NK131(do)002:357: gyi khams su gtogs pa la mi mjed 'jig rten
NK131(do)002:358: ngo mi shes pa'i gtam yin pa 'dra sems zhes
NK131(do)002:359: bshad 'dug pa / pa'i lan ni / tshig bsdus pa ma gtogs /
NK131(do)002:360: mi mjed 'jig rten gyi mtho sa nas dma' sa der dor ba'i don yin /
NK131(do)002:362: zhi gnas spangs te zung 'brel bsgom par shog /
NK131(do)002:364: gzhan dga' ldan mi mjed 'jig rten na yod pa sus kyang shes mod kyi /
NK131(do)002:365: tshig sbyor brjod bde phyir gsungs pa la 'gal ba med de bshes spring las /
NK131(do)002:366: kha cig lcags las byas pa'i zangs chen du //
NK131(do)002:368: lcags yin na zangs yin par bud //
NK131(do)002:370: de yang brjod pa dang go sla ba'i phyir bshad pas /
NK131(do)002:372: spyir thang yig la sogs sngags gtso phyir gsungs pa la /
NK131(do)002:373: mdo sde sogs drang ldem sna tshogs kyi rtogs pa /
NK131(do)002:374: ti thug rigs 'dre lta bur sbyor bar byed na
NK131(do)002:375: dpyad kyis mi long bas thugs las chung ngur bag
NK131(do)002:376: phob cig / yang rgyal po spyan med 'byor ldan gyi le'u skabs su /
NK131(do)002:377: dbang po'i dngas ma mig ni nga la med ces bshad pas de'i 'og tsam na /
NK131(do)002:378: rgyal pos nor bu len par phyin nas tshong pa rnams rin po che'i gling du bzhag /
NK131(do)002:379: rgyal po dang ded dpon gnyis gru chung gcig tu zhugs te phyin pa las /
NK131(do)002:380: rgyal pos ri dkar po zhig mthong ste /
NK131(do)002:381: pha gi ci yi ri yin dris pas /
NK131(do)002:382: ded dpon gyis dngul gyi ri yin zhes lan btab pa dang /
NK131(do)002:383: de nas gser gyi ri dang /
NK131(do)002:384: bee d+aur+ya'i ri yang mthong bar bshad pas mig yod par bshad 'dug pa dang /
NK131(do)002:385: yang de'i 'og tsam na nor bus mig g.yon pa
NK131(do)002:386: bye bar bshad 'dug pas gang dran dran bris pa
NK131(do)002:388: 'di 'dra'i skabs kyi spyan med ces pa dgos pa'i dbang gis sprul pa yin pas /
NK131(do)002:389: deng sang gi long ba phal pa dang ga la
NK131(do)002:390: 'dra sangs rgyas kyi 'khrungs rabs tshor bram ze long
NK131(do)002:391: ba la mig byin nas sbyar bar mig byung ba
NK131(do)002:392: sogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas yin mod /
NK131(do)002:393: deng sang mi gcig gis mig phyung nas /
NK131(do)002:394: mig med pa gcig la yong gnag rdzi rgan po yan chad kyis shes mod /
NK131(do)002:395: dpe de rgyu mtshan du byas nas /
NK131(do)002:396: sangs rgyas kyi 'khrungs rabs la yang skur pa 'debs sam dngos lan yang /
NK131(do)002:397: dang po rgyal po la mig med /
NK131(do)002:398: nor bu len du byon skabs /
NK131(do)002:399: mig dngos su ma phye yang /
NK131(do)002:400: smon lam dang bsod nams kyi mthus /
NK131(do)002:401: rags pa'i yul snang gsal ba tsam byung bar bshad de /
NK131(do)002:403: smon lam stobs kyis rgyal po'i mthong yul du rags
NK131(do)002:404: pa'i yul snang cung zhig gsal bar gyur bltas pas
NK131(do)002:405: ri ni dkar po zhig snang ste zhes gsungs la
NK131(do)002:407: nor bu len nas gsol ba btab pas spyan g.yon bye /
NK131(do)002:408: o rgyan dang mjal bas g.yas bye ba sogs bshad pas /
NK131(do)002:409: 'gal rkyen spu tsam yang med par tshad mas grub pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)002:411: 'od srungs rgan pos lcang lo bsil ba na //
NK131(do)002:412: zhes bshad 'dug pa la 'od srungs rang ga ba zhig yin na ma tog /
NK131(do)002:413: nyan thos 'od srungs chen po ni bcom ldan 'das kyis bstan pa gtad de /
NK131(do)002:414: bstan pa'i bdag po yin pas /
NK131(do)002:415: de skra breg bcug nas kun dga' bo la rab
NK131(do)002:416: tu byung ba'i tshul dang mi mthun pa zhig go
NK131(do)002:417: // lhag par ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo brgyad nas o rgyan 'byung bar bshad /
NK131(do)002:418: rgyal po lo lnga bsil ba tshal du lo lnga
NK131(do)002:419: ste kun dga' bo dang mjal dus ston pa mya
NK131(do)002:420: ngan las 'das nas lo bco brgyad po 'dug pa
NK131(do)002:421: dang / 'od srungs chen po ston pa mya ngan
NK131(do)002:422: las 'das pa'i phyir lo bka' bsdu dang po byas
NK131(do)002:423: te bya rkang gi ri la mya ngan las 'das
NK131(do)002:424: dang / pas / rgyus med zhig gis pho tshod byas pa 'dra sems /
NK131(do)002:426: spyir le'u nyer gnyis bsil tshal du bzhugs pa'i le'u
NK131(do)002:427: yin pas rab tu byung ba'i 'phros med la le'u
NK131(do)002:428: nyer drug pa rab tu byung ba'i le'u skabs su
NK131(do)002:435: 'od srungs byis pa can sogs rnam grangs du ma bshad pas /
NK131(do)002:436: 'od srungs gcig po de las med snyam pa mi dgos shing /
NK131(do)002:437: bka' bsdu gsum pa'i skabs su yang /
NK131(do)002:438: grong khyer skya bo'i phur gnas brtan 'od srungs chen
NK131(do)002:439: po dang bla ma la sogs pa yod pa'i lugs
NK131(do)002:440: kyang bu ston chos 'byung las bshad pas de 'dra'i
NK131(do)002:442: gal te 'od srungs chen po yin kyang des skra breg bcug nas /
NK131(do)002:443: kun dgas mkhan po byed pa mi rigs rgyu med de /
NK131(do)002:445: khyim bdag dpal skyes lo brgya nyi shu lon pa rab tu byung ba'i tshe /
NK131(do)002:446: nyan thos la mi shes pa'i rgyu bzhi yod pas /
NK131(do)002:447: dpal skyes kyis thar pa'i sa bon ma shes par
NK131(do)002:448: nyan thos sus kyang rab tu ma phyung bar des
NK131(do)002:449: ngus pas / ston pas dbugs phyungs te sus 'dul gzigs pas /
NK131(do)002:450: moo gal gyi bus 'dul bar gzigs nas /
NK131(do)002:451: nyan thos kyi gdul bya sangs rgyas kyis mi 'dul /
NK131(do)002:452: sangs rgyas kyi gdul bya nyan thos kyis mi 'dul bas ston pas zhu ba lta bu mdzad /
NK131(do)002:453: moo gal gyis rab tu byung ba yin pas /
NK131(do)002:454: de la yang bstan pa'i bdag po ston pas rab tu mi 'byin par /
NK131(do)002:455: moo gal gyis rab tu byung ba mi rigs zhes zer ram /
NK131(do)002:456: thang yig tu 'od srungs rgan po zer ba tsam las /
NK131(do)002:457: rgyal tshab 'od srungs yin zhes pa'i gsal kha med /
NK131(do)002:458: kun dga' bo'i nyan thos kyi khrod du na tshod
NK131(do)002:459: rgan ming la 'od srungs zer ba zhig med pa'i
NK131(do)002:461: de 'dra'i sbugs 'thum na shes bya mtha' bkag par 'gro bas /
NK131(do)002:462: gsang phu ba tsho'i zhabs 'dren mi gnang ba zhu /
NK131(do)002:463: lo grangs mi 'grigs pa'i log rtog kyang mtha' gcig tu 'dzin na bden mod kyang /
NK131(do)002:464: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi mdzad pa ni /
NK131(do)002:465: bskal pa skad cig mar bsgyur ba dang skad cig
NK131(do)002:466: ma bskal par bsgyur ba sogs mdzad pas byis pas
NK131(do)002:467: nam mkha'i tshad bzung lta ci dgos la /
NK131(do)002:468: gzhan du ston pa'i 'das lo rtsi ba'i tshe yang /
NK131(do)002:469: mdo rgyud dang mkhas pa so so'i lugs mi 'dra
NK131(do)002:470: ba mang bas mi 'grigs pa mang bar 'dug pa
NK131(do)002:471: rnams thugs su gsal las che bas /
NK131(do)002:472: de dag dang mtshungs par blta'o //
NK131(do)002:473: yang sh+aakya seng ger mtshan gsol ba yang de ni
NK131(do)002:474: ston pa'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs yin pas sangs rgyas
NK131(do)002:475: zin kyang de'i rjes su rab tu byung ba yin
NK131(do)002:476: pas ston pa'i mtshan nas 'dogs pa yang /
NK131(do)002:477: the tshom gyi gnas zhig go //
NK131(do)002:479: 'o na deng sang pa dge'i grwa khrod du yang kun dga' rgyal mtshan dang /
NK131(do)002:480: blo bzang grags pa sogs rje btsun so so de
NK131(do)002:481: dag gis mtshan btags pa mang po yong gi 'dug
NK131(do)002:482: / lar tha mal pa yang ming mtha' bkag pa'i nyams kyi /
NK131(do)002:483: nang po sangs rgyas 'brogs pa sangs rgyas zhes btags pa mang bas /
NK131(do)002:484: de mi rung zhes 'jig rten grags pa'i tshod sus 'gog nus //
NK131(do)002:485: skabs 'dir ni o rgyan chen po sangs rgyas nyid
NK131(do)002:486: dang zhal gnyis pa lta bu yin pas sh+aakya seng
NK131(do)002:487: ge'i mtshan shin tu gsol rung /
NK131(do)002:488: yang sangs rgyas kyi mtshan la sh+aakya'i rgyal po yang zer ba 'dug pas /
NK131(do)002:489: des na sh+aakya'i rigs kyi rgyal srid 'dzin pa rnams kyang mtshan gcig par 'gro /
NK131(do)002:490: 'gro ba'i rgyu mtshan rgyal po de dag sh+aakya'i rigs yin pas /
NK131(do)002:491: sh+aakya yin par gang zhig rgyal sar gnas pas rgyal po las 'os med pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)002:492: spyir bstan pa'i rjes 'jug yin pas kyang ma 'gal te /
NK131(do)002:493: da ltar gyi cho ga'i ming barje ba'i dus /
NK131(do)002:494: sde pa so so'i ming yang thog mthar 'dogs par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)002:495: 'phags yul gyi sh+aakya 'od dang sh+aakya blo /
NK131(do)002:496: bod kyi gser mdog can la /
NK131(do)002:497: sh+aakya mchog ldan sogs mang bas de dag la yang skur 'debs ma gnang bar zhu /
NK131(do)002:498: yang le'u nyer gsum par chos 'khor dang po'i nang du /
NK131(do)002:499: karma sha tam mdo rtsa ba /
NK131(do)002:500: ka ri kha gsum brgya pa sogs kyi bstan bcos grangs 'dug pas ma 'grigs pa 'dra sems /
NK131(do)002:502: le'u nyer gsum pa rtsis la sbyangs pa'i le'u yin pas /
NK131(do)002:504: le'u brgyad cu gya bzhi bar sgra bsgyur ba mdzad tshul gyi skabs su /
NK131(do)002:505: bka' dang bstan bcos rnams bsgyur tshul 'chad tshe /
NK131(do)002:507: karma sha tam sogs 'dul ba'i gras su bsdus te bshad pa las /
NK131(do)002:508: bka' yin zhes bshad pa ni med do //
NK131(do)002:510: thub dbang yongs su mya ngan 'das bar du sangs
NK131(do)002:511: rgyas gsung rnams yi ger thebs tshad btab ces sangs
NK131(do)002:512: rgyas mya ngan las 'das ma thag /
NK131(do)002:513: gsung rab brjed dgos nas glegs bam du bkod par bshad 'dug pa /
NK131(do)002:514: gsung rab glegs bam du bkod pa ni /
NK131(do)002:515: bka' bsdu gsum pa'i dus yin pa ni mkhas pa
NK131(do)002:516: phal che ba bzhed cing bka' bsdu dang po'i dus
NK131(do)002:517: su ni sde snod yi ger btab pa ni tshad
NK131(do)002:518: ldan gyi lung las bshad pa med /
NK131(do)002:519: 'on kyang bka' bsdu ba dang po gnyis pa byed
NK131(do)002:520: pa'i dus su dgra bcom pa dang pan+di ta mi
NK131(do)002:521: brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa rnams kyis /
NK131(do)002:522: sde snod gsum rang rang gi blo nas brjod pa lags pas /
NK131(do)002:523: 'di yang 'ol tshod ma 'grigs pa zhig yin nam /
NK131(do)002:525: le'u nyer bzhi sman la sbyangs pa'i le'u yin la /
NK131(do)002:526: nyer brgyad pa kun dga' bo la mdo dris pa'i skabs su de ltar bshad /
NK131(do)002:527: 'on kyang bka' bsdu'i skor 'di tsho 'dul ba sogs theg dman gyi skabs yin pas /
NK131(do)002:528: der bka' bsdu mtha' ma'i tshe ma togs yi ger ma bris pa 'dra shin tu 'dug rung /
NK131(do)002:529: rgyu mtshan gcig po de ka la chags bzhag na /
NK131(do)002:530: kha che bye brag smra ba sogs /
NK131(do)002:531: theg chen gyi sde snod rnams klu sgrub dang thogs
NK131(do)002:532: med kyis rang bzo mdzad zer chag lo chos rje
NK131(do)002:533: dpal gyis brgyad stong pa'i rgya dpe zhig bsnams nas
NK131(do)002:534: byon pas / rdo rje gdan gyi dkor gnyer gyis /
NK131(do)002:535: chos log de 'dra khur nas zer ba yang 'dug /
NK131(do)002:536: bka' thams cad dus gcig po de las gzhan du ma bsdus na rgyud rnams kyang /
NK131(do)002:537: bka' yin pas der khas len dgos /
NK131(do)002:538: de ltar na gsang ba las kyang ches gsang ba
NK131(do)002:539: de dag nyan thos sogs la yongs su grags pa
NK131(do)002:540: yin 'dug pas ngo mtshar shin tu che /
NK131(do)002:541: gzhan yang kun dga' bo mngon shes dang ldan pa
NK131(do)002:542: yin pas dus der glegs bam du byas ma zin
NK131(do)002:543: kyang / ma 'ongs pa na 'gyur 'gyur ma gsungs pa'i nges pa ci yod /
NK131(do)002:544: gzhan yang 'jam dpal rtsa rgyud las /
NK131(do)002:545: ma skyes dgra'i bu u pa zhes bya bas /
NK131(do)002:546: sangs rgyas kyi gsung rab rnams yi ger 'bri bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)002:549: bcom ldan 'das yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK131(do)002:550: sdud par byed pa po dag gi theg pa gsum glegs bam la bris te /
NK131(do)002:552: mtha' gcig tu nges pa med do //
NK131(do)002:553: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngal sgo 'grim zhes pa gcig kyang 'dug pa /
NK131(do)002:554: sangs rgyas ni yum gyi rtsibs logs nas bltams pa rgyus med pa'i pho tshod yin pa 'dra /
NK131(do)002:556: dus gsum sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku thams cad mdzad
NK131(do)002:557: pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul ston par mngal skyes la
NK131(do)002:558: ma brten par lhums su zhugs bltams pa sogs byed
NK131(do)002:559: thabs med la / de dag mngal skyes ma yin na /
NK131(do)002:560: bardzusa skyes sgong skyes drod gsher skyes gsum gang yin khyed la 'adri'o //
NK131(do)002:561: rtsibs logs nas bltams kyang don mngal skyes yin te /
NK131(do)002:562: mo mtshan la mngal du 'dzin pa ni 'khrul pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)002:563: mdor na dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyi yum gyi
NK131(do)002:564: kha sna gsang gshang gang las bltams kyang yum la
NK131(do)002:565: brten phyir mngal skyes las mi 'ada'o //
NK131(do)002:568: lo re bzhin du dbang bskur byin rlabs zhus lo
NK131(do)002:569: brgya lon na dbang brgya thob pa yin phyi ma
NK131(do)002:570: dud 'gror skyes kyang dbang chen skyes zhes bshad 'dug
NK131(do)002:571: pa dbang zhes pa lam bsgom pa la dbang ba
NK131(do)002:572: yin pas 'di ni 'jig rten pa'i rgan mo gcig
NK131(do)002:576: bi ma las rdzu 'phrul ston pa'i le'u yin la /
NK131(do)002:577: brgya dang lnga pa gung thang la khar snga 'gros btang ba'i le'u las /
NK131(do)002:579: lo re bzhin dbang tshar re zhus pa'i mi de
NK131(do)002:580: lo brgya lon nas dbang brgya los thob pas skyon
NK131(do)002:581: ci 'jug / spyir gsang sngags kyi dbang bskur ba
NK131(do)002:582: lam gang dang gang yin de bsgom pa la dbang
NK131(do)002:584: de'i zhar la 'bras lo legs nas r+ts+wa dang phub ma 'byung ba lta bur /
NK131(do)002:585: thun mong gi dngos grub kyang 'byung ba yin /
NK131(do)002:586: dbang mang du thob pa zhig dud 'gror skyes na
NK131(do)002:587: rten de la la ma bsgom pa'i nus pa med
NK131(do)002:588: mod / 'on kyang dge ba'i mthu des dud 'gro'i
NK131(do)002:589: nang nas dbang che ba khyu mchog lta bur skyes
NK131(do)002:590: na longs spyod rgya cher 'byung ba yang dag gam
NK131(do)002:591: mod / / khyed rang dpon slob rmi ru ba
NK131(do)002:592: zhal ngo tsho sbyin bdag gcig gi nang du kun
NK131(do)002:593: mod / / rig gi bstod / gcig gi nang du sked pa /
NK131(do)002:596: dud 'gror skyes kyang dbang chung chung rang las yong ba mi 'dug /
NK131(do)002:597: kha yongs su byed na dbang zhes pa lam bsgom pa la dbang ba gcig pur ma nges /
NK131(do)002:598: dbang bskur ba rgyur byas te /
NK131(do)002:599: so so'i lam bsgom pas 'bras bu sku gsum la
NK131(do)002:600: dbang bas rgyu lam 'bras bu'i dbang zhes kyang bya
NK131(do)002:602: gang zag dbang thob pa de /
NK131(do)002:603: las nag gi 'bras bu phra mos ngan song dud 'gro lta bur skyes pa na /
NK131(do)002:604: dbang thob pa'i rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu dbang cher skye bas don de la dgongs pa yin la /
NK131(do)002:605: 'phen byed sdig pa dud 'gror 'phongs rdzogs byed dge bas dbang cher skyes pa yang yin te /
NK131(do)002:607: 'phen byed sdig la rdzogs byed dge //
NK131(do)002:609: de'i dpe don lhan gcig tu ston pa'i tshe //
NK131(do)002:611: de yi lus sems bde ba yi //
NK131(do)002:612: gnas skabs dge bas 'phongs par gsungs //
NK131(do)002:614: gzhan yang rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ci snyam na /
NK131(do)002:615: las la dge sdig lung ma bstan //
NK131(do)002:616: yin zhes rgyal bas mdo las gsungs //
NK131(do)002:618: dge sdig gnyis la rang rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK131(do)002:620: 'bras bu la dbye na gnyis te gnas skabs dang mthar thug gnyis /
NK131(do)002:621: de la yang rnam smin gyi 'bras bu /
NK131(do)002:623: mthar thug gi 'bras bu ste gsum /
NK131(do)002:627: de la yang dper mtshon na /
NK131(do)002:628: srog gcod lta bu ngo bo /
NK131(do)002:629: de'i 'bras bu mthar thug tu dmyal ba /
NK131(do)002:631: rnam smin ni mthar thug rgyu mthun gnyis kyi myong ba rgyun ni gnas skabs dang 'dra /
NK131(do)002:632: byed pa ni tshe rabs su srog gcod pa la dga'/
NK131(do)002:633: bdag po'i 'bras bu phyi rol gyi yul la smin
NK131(do)002:634: pa sogs bshad pas rgyas par mdo lung dri med
NK131(do)002:637: klu sgrub yab sras kyi gsung rab sogs las 'byung
NK131(do)002:638: ba ltar legs par gzigs nas don thugs su chud
NK131(do)002:639: par mdzad du gsol zhes gsol ba snying nas 'debs
NK131(do)002:640: pa lags / yang dbang las 'bras rnam bshad 'di rnams /
NK131(do)002:641: lha sa sde bzhir dbang bskur chos bshad gnang dus makho'am snyam thugs bskyed yong res bris pa lags /
NK131(do)002:643: 'di rigs la zad pa mi 'dug pas phyogs gnyis
NK131(do)002:644: kas rtogs sla ba rnams yi ger bris pa lags
NK131(do)002:645: / gsung pa ni thugs bden te thugs kyi 'dzin stangs gzhan du gzhol ba'i dbang gis /
NK131(do)002:646: o rgyan chen pos ji mdzad thams cad log par
NK131(do)002:647: song ba 'dra zhing byung 'dug pas bzod par gsol
NK131(do)002:648: / gzhan yang ma ni bka' 'bum sogs kyi lan yang gong dang 'dra bas /
NK131(do)002:649: gzu bor gnas pa'i blo dpyad na /
NK131(do)002:650: dpyad rgyu ci yang med mod /
NK131(do)002:651: 'on kyang log rtog gi mtha' la 'dzad pa mi
NK131(do)002:652: 'dug pas zhus kyi mi long bar re zhig bzhag
NK131(do)002:653: go // spyir mkhas pa'i gsung rab barlinga zhing don
NK131(do)002:654: che ba brtan pa tsam gyis blo'i gsos su gyur
NK131(do)002:655: go // pa dag ni / bstan pa'i byi dor yin pas /
NK131(do)002:656: rang cag blo gros kyi mthu chung yang skal ba 'jog phyir 'bel gtam gling bar smon yang /
NK131(do)002:657: kun slong skyon can ngan pas rgyu bsdoms pa'i dri
NK131(do)002:658: ba za zi barlanga tshig gya tshoms su smra ba
NK131(do)002:659: la snying po ci zhig yod /
NK131(do)002:661: snga 'gyur gyi ring lugs bzang por kun nas smod pa'i tshig dor te /
NK131(do)002:662: dag pa'i snang ba sbyangs na legs te /
NK131(do)002:664: gang zhig yang yang sdig grogs brten nas sangs rgyas ngan sems ldan gyur cing //
NK131(do)002:665: pha ma dgra bcom gsad par bya ba min byed tshogs mchog 'byed pa'i mi //
NK131(do)002:666: de yang chos nyid nges par bsams na myur du de las thar gyur te //
NK131(do)002:667: gang zhig yid ni chos la sdang ba de la thar pa ga la yod //
NK131(do)002:670: chos kyi mtshan nyid gang la yod med dag /
NK131(do)002:671: mi shes mthong ba med par rgyu bzhi yis //
NK131(do)002:672: rnam dbye smra ba'i kha ni bdud kyis phye //
NK131(do)002:673: chos la nyes smod thub pa'i gzhung las bkag /
NK131(do)002:675: bu ston thams cad mkhyen pas /
NK131(do)002:676: rang nyid grags 'dod pha rol dma' dbab 'dod //
NK131(do)002:677: g.yo sgyu'i rtsod pa 'di yang dmyal ba'i rgyu //
NK131(do)002:678: zhes gsungs pa shin tu bden par snang ste /
NK131(do)002:679: rtsod pa phal cher chags sdang rmongs gsum gyis kun nas bslangs pa ma rtogs mi gda' bas /
NK131(do)002:680: sems can dmyal ba'i rgyu las 'os ci yod /
NK131(do)002:681: khyad par dam pa'i rnam thar la gshe skur btab
NK131(do)002:682: na lce la lcags kyi thong pa me 'bar bas
NK131(do)002:683: smod pa sogs 'od srungs rdzogs byed kyi gtam rgyud
NK131(do)002:685: 'bras bu mi zad pa'i duhkha la 'jigs sems kyi rgyu la blang dor mdzad par rigs so //
NK131(do)002:686: snga 'gyur theg pa kun gyi rtse yin kyang //
NK131(do)002:687: deng dus ches cher snyigs pa'i bskal ngan gyis //
NK131(do)002:688: phal cher log par blta ba'i mig nad can //
NK131(do)002:689: zas la skra shad ltar mthong dngos po'i gshis //
NK131(do)002:690: sa dge kar gnyis grub pa'i mtha' kun gyis //
NK131(do)002:691: tshad mar byed pa'i bka' gdams glegs bam las //
NK131(do)002:692: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed bdag pos byin rlabs pa'i //
NK131(do)002:693: mkhas rlom la la bstings tshig skur pa 'debs //
NK131(do)002:694: skyon kun yongs bral zas gtsang sras po la //
NK131(do)002:695: mu stegs byed sogs smod pa lhur len na //
NK131(do)002:696: deng dus bdud kyi rnam par phye ba'i kha //
NK131(do)002:697: mthu chen gsang bdag des kyang zum nus min //
NK131(do)002:698: de phyin dngos 'dras bskal lan 'debs pa sogs //
NK131(do)002:699: gzhan don mi 'gyur rang nyid ngal ba'i rgyu //
NK131(do)002:700: yin phyir spros pa dor te rang mal du //
NK131(do)002:701: rtse gcig mnyam par bzhag na legs par mngon //
NK131(do)002:702: 'on te gzhung lugs rgya mtsho'i pha rol du //
NK131(do)002:703: nyer son mkhas pa'i dbang po khyod nyid kyis //
NK131(do)002:704: brgal brtags mdzad pa rgyal bstan rin chen la //
NK131(do)002:705: byi dor yin phyir nyes pa'i skyon ci zhig /
NK131(do)002:706: nged cag skyes sbyangs rnam dpyod stobs phra yang //
NK131(do)002:707: bshes gnyen mkhas pa'i gsung gi lan 'debs pa //
NK131(do)002:708: bskal pa bzang phyir rtse gcig brtson pa yis //
NK131(do)002:709: 'bad de legs bshad nyung ngu 'di brtsams so //
NK131(do)002:710: 'di sbyar ngal ba'i dge des 'gro rmongs kyi //
NK131(do)002:711: sdug bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa gtan bcom ste //
NK131(do)002:712: mnyam med stobs bcu mnga' ba'i go 'phang la //
NK131(do)002:713: 'khod nas don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK131(do)002:714: lhag bsam chu 'dzin stug por 'khrigs pa'i dbus //
NK131(do)002:715: lung rigs dbyar gyi rnga chen rab sgrog cing //
NK131(do)002:716: rtsod tshig gnam lcags 'bar ba'i me dbal gyi //
NK131(do)002:717: phas rgol log rtog thal bar rlog byed shog /
NK131(do)002:718: dge 'dis thub bstan snying po snga 'gyur gzhung //
NK131(do)002:719: dri med bka' gter chos kyi nyin byed kyis //
NK131(do)002:720: skye dgu'i mi shes mun pa rab bsal nas //
NK131(do)002:721: bstan 'dzin 'dab brgya grol ba'i dge legs shog //
NK131(do)002:722: de ltar rtsod bzlog gnam lcags 'brug brgya dgod pa'i nga ro zhes bya ba 'di yang /
NK131(do)002:723: lha sa sbus srang nas thos ldan a bo skyon pa lags kyi gsung gis bskul ngor /
NK131(do)002:724: pad+ma'i rjes 'jug bka' gdams kyi dge slong pad+ma phrin las kyis /
NK131(do)002:725: sa ga'i dmar phyogs rgyal ba gsum pa'i tshes la /
NK131(do)002:726: rang gnas thub bstan rdo rje brag gi chos grwar sbyar ba dge /
